{"tid":495260,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係第一代安安，有D嘢想講下","createTime":"2017-12-10T14:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T17:38:15.000Z","uid":38703,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"24ba141d7832edeccefcc3a40fa3ef4c2ea58447","tid":495260,"uid":38703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"呢兩個星期睇到大家玩佳佳，返工辛苦得嚟都可以笑下好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n第一次撚佳佳時，未必係個個都中意，甚至大部分人都覺得Season 1係爛尾，某程度上我都覺得唔算撚得好好，亦同意大家對我嘅意見。<br />\n<br />\n我就係唔想扮老屎忽同埋想大家自由發展，所以咁多個Season都只係睇後來嘅安安撚佳佳，無乜講太多意見。只係我唔明好多小學雞下下都叫安安自爆、話自己係公安/香港警察，又有人係咪都話安安沉船，心諗佢哋做乜鳩。<br />\n<br />\n無論點都好，連登係值得有多D比撚佳佳Post甚至撚雞Post高質嘅創意Post，好希望大家好好建立連登。<br />\n<br />\n例如舊登初期D改圖Post好好笑，學術台都學到好多嘢，氣象Post一樣，希望到我下年上連登氣象Post時，唔好個個都一味問人幾點掛波落波咁低質。<br />\n<br />\n要記住，我哋係香港人，即使網上網下，都要保持高質。如果唔係，同香討果班戇鳩仔有乜撚嘢分別？<br />\n<br />\nBTW，間唔中睇到D騙子崩潰好好笑，我諗佢哋無諗過會被人撚返轉頭。好多謝後來嘅安安為我哋帶來歡樂"},{"pid":"2e75a57b4fa0a56689fd95946195c94d06dea422","tid":495260,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"0c1c685dda23c9cb4d747b46dd35596fbcdfda0d","tid":495260,"uid":25319,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"躝"},{"pid":"e2b97b664b58f73c29b43c5942f4ae0cf936d609","tid":495260,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"真係多謝你俾大家可以自由發揮"},{"pid":"91657e74f9f24a60a797c1e95b1a9d13f9de5429","tid":495260,"uid":137890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"Ching 好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba40b163789a65163db427947f6f0b5653088bf","tid":495260,"uid":2901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ccba99edd8d47dfc92b532fdd99431ccfc3abb","tid":495260,"uid":57776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"睇得開心咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗理d小學雞"},{"pid":"4023631f269c4d06f152fe00b6e603d57f5ce620","tid":495260,"uid":31778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"最難得你唔會老屎忽 肯放手俾之後嘅安安玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}